00:41:03.735 --> 00:41:05.601
I’d rather you be the truth.

00:41:06.405 --> 00:41:08.753
The truth that no one can take you away from me.

00:41:09.445 --> 00:41:11.769
The link between the two is

00:41:12.405 --> 00:41:14.577
they both used to work for the Thayadon family.

00:41:15.325 --> 00:41:16.873
I’m taking up the case because of you.

00:41:16.905 --> 00:41:17.217
LIKE.

00:41:17.525 --> 00:41:19.009
Who would ever let their first love

00:41:19.033 --> 00:41:20.553
go through such a dreadful case alone?

00:41:21.535 --> 00:41:24.505
Look for infamous news about Botpleng’s father.

00:41:25.205 --> 00:41:26.205
Dig deep.

00:41:26.635 --> 00:41:27.681
Tonight…

00:41:28.235 --> 00:41:29.321
Can I sleep with you?

00:41:32.365 --> 00:41:33.377
I just want to

00:41:34.635 --> 00:41:36.065
relive the memory.

00:41:41.845 --> 00:41:43.593
You’re looking for your older brother, right?

00:41:43.617 --> 00:41:44.921
The one who’s with you now

00:41:44.961 --> 00:41:46.297
is not Tankhun.

00:41:46.825 --> 00:41:49.089
That’s why you can’t remember him.

00:41:49.105 --> 00:41:51.521
Even if I don’t have the memory of 10 years ago,

00:41:51.561 --> 00:41:53.969
I think I have made new memories now.

00:41:54.345 --> 00:41:55.345
I like you.

00:41:55.655 --> 00:41:57.095
Will you please never be gone again?